<p>I adore SCP fiction and this community. I find it difficult to believe I'd ever permanently lose interest, but you never know. If I become inactive for 1.75 continuous years, and any of my works become considered not up to community standards for whatever reason, I give my blessing for any experienced author to attempt a rewrite.</p>
